import { Card, Col, Row } from "react-bootstrap"; import '../UserCard/style.css'; import riderImage from '../Assets/charan.jpg' import axios from "axios"; interface props { rideId: number; rideProviderId: string; sourceId: number; destinationId: number; date: string; fair: number; totalSeats: number; availableSeats: number; time: string; seatsBooked:number; } const UserCard: React.FC = ({ rideId, rideProviderId, sourceId, destinationId, date, fair, totalSeats, availableSeats, time,seatsBooked }) => { const userData = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("userData")!) const userId = userData.loginId; const addBookRideToBackend = async () => { await axios.post('https://localhost:7243/api/BookRide/Booking', { "customerId": userId, "rideId": rideId, "seatsBooked": seatsBooked } ) .then(e => console.log(e)) .catch(error => console.log(error)) } return ( { addBookRideToBackend() }}>
